Design System Overview
1. Color System
CSS custom properties with light/dark mode support:
Light Mode:
--bg: white
--text-headings: black
--text-body: #000000d9 (89% opacity)
--text-secondary: #000000aa (67% opacity)
--bg-button: #000000
--text-button: #ffffff
--border-input: #00000055 (33% opacity)
--border-card: #000000aa (67% opacity)
--shadow-ava: #000000bd (74% opacity)
Dark Mode:
--bg: #141414
--text-headings: white
--text-body: #ffffffd9 (85% opacity)
--text-secondary: #ffffffaa (67% opacity)
--bg-button: white
--text-button: #000000
--border-input: #ffffff55 (33% opacity)
--border-card: #ffffffaa (67% opacity)
--shadow-ava: #ffffff8c (55% opacity)
2. Typography System
Font Family:
Base font: Manrope, "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif
Typography Components (Styled Components):
Heading1:
Desktop: 36px, 700, line-height 49px, letter-spacing -0.025em
Mobile: 32px, line-height 36px
Heading2: 30px, 700, letter-spacing -0.025em
Heading3: 24px, 600, letter-spacing -0.025em
Paragraph:
Desktop: 18px, 400, line-height 31px
Mobile: 16px, line-height 28px
SubParagraph: 14px, 400, line-height 25px
AltText: 14px, italic, uses --text-secondary
3. Spacing System
Common spacing values:
8px - Small padding/gaps
16px - Standard gap
24px - Medium spacing
32px - Large gap
40px - Section spacing
48px - Major section spacing
64px - Large section spacing
128px - Extra large section spacing (used in Home page)
Layout patterns:
Max width container: 1200px (from App.module.scss)
Blog detail max width: 693px
Body padding: 0 1.0875rem 1.45rem (mobile)
4. Component Patterns
Cards:
No border-radius (border-radius: 0)
Hover effects: image scale 1.05
Border: 0.25px solid var(--border-card)
Hover shadow: 6px 6px var(--shadow-ava) with translate transform
Buttons:
Background: var(--bg-button)
Color: var(--text-button)
Font: 700, uppercase, letter-spacing 2px
Padding: 10px 24px (primary) or 8px (form buttons)
Shadow: 6px 6px var(--shadow-ava)
Hover: translate -6px -6px, shadow 12px 12px
Active: translate 3px 3px, shadow 3px 3px
Inputs:
Border: 0.25px solid var(--border-input)
No border-radius (border-radius: 0)
Padding: 8px
Font: 500, 0.875rem (14px)
Focus: shadow 4px 4px var(--shadow-ava)
Background: transparent
Grids:
Blog cards: 3 columns → 2 columns (≤1080px) → 1 column (≤550px)
Gap: 3rem columns, 4rem rows (desktop), 2rem rows (mobile)
Message wall: 3 columns (33.3% width) → 1 column (mobile)
Gutter: 15px (height and width)
5. Animation Patterns
Framer Motion:
Common variants: hidden: { opacity: 0, y: -100 }, visible: { opacity: 1, y: 0 }
Easing: anticipate
Duration: 0.5s - 1s
Stagger delays: 0.25s, 0.5s, 0.75s
Hover animations:
Scale: 1.05 for images
Transform: translateX(-6px) translateY(-6px) for buttons/cards
Shadow increase on hover
6. Responsive Breakpoints
Mobile: ≤475px, ≤550px, ≤720px, ≤800px
Tablet: ≤1080px
Desktop: >1080px
Mobile adjustments:
Typography scales down
Flex direction changes to column
Margins/padding reduce
Grids collapse to single column
7. Design Principles
No border-radius (sharp corners)
Bold shadows using --shadow-ava
High contrast text (headings vs body)
Consistent spacing scale (8px base)
Smooth transitions (0.2s - 0.5s)
Dark mode via CSS variables
Mobile-first responsive design
8. Styling Approach
Styled Components: Typography, complex components
SCSS Modules: Page-specific styles, component modules
CSS Variables: Theme colors, consistent theming
Tailwind: Utility classes (with preflight: false)